# after you've created a new user there a different ways to login as this user.
# In graphic session (Gnome) you can go to the top right corner, press power button and then choose switch user option
# after that you choose freshly created user and enter his password.
# alternatively you can type the command "su new_user" and login as that user with terminal
# you also can do something like "ssh -p 1222 new_user@hostname"